creator: Keyflow
descriptionHtml:
Find out what’s on in your city, send requests for a night out and take a time out. Don’t risk ruin your party mood by being left outside - let Keyflow be your guide to a fun nightclub experience.
Explore, find and get access to events and private parties with our state of the art app! Standing in line at the club was yesterday. Purchase tickets to your favorite events, send guest list- and VIP table requests and get a confirmation faster than ever. Sit back and relax while we present your profile to the venue. Once the venue responds to your request - we notify you in real-time!
Feeling bold? Keyflow now offers for you as a user to upload and apply to go to private parties. Feel like adding some extra spice to your pre-party, your VIP-table or why not your after-party? Through Keyflow Konnect we allow our users to upload and share their private party activity to other users. Just like Tinder you’ll swipe right or left to accept or reject users that’ve requested to join!
With the feature - “Go out tonight” you’re able to send a request to multiple venues at the same time. The first venue to accept your request is the one to welcome you.
Keyflow connects venues and guests globally in cities across Europe and in the Middle East by opening the doors to some of the world’s most luxurious entertainment options. Does your venue want to become part of the ever-growing Keyflow network? Contact sales@keyflow.com.

Explore, find and get access to events and private parties with our state of the art app! Standing in line at the club was yesterday. Purchase tickets to your favorite events, send guest list- and VIP table requests and get a confirmation faster than ever. Sit back and relax while we present your profile to the venue. Once the venue responds to your request - we notify you in real-time!

Feeling bold? Keyflow now offers for you as a user to upload and apply to go to private parties. Feel like adding some extra spice to your pre-party, your VIP-table or why not your after-party? Through Keyflow Konnect we allow our users to upload and share their private party activity to other users. Just like Tinder you’ll swipe right or left to accept or reject users that’ve requested to join!

With the feature - “Go out tonight” you’re able to send a request to multiple venues at the same time. The first venue to accept your request is the one to welcome you.

Keyflow connects venues and guests globally in cities across Europe and in the Middle East by opening the doors to some of the world’s most luxurious entertainment options. Does your venue want to become part of the ever-growing Keyflow network? Contact sales@keyflow.com.
descriptionShort: Explore, create and get access to events, nightclubs and private parties!

title: Keyflow: Your key to nightlife

creator: Keyflow
descriptionHtml:
Discover the best nightlife Scandinavia has to offer with the Keyflow app. Boasting a community of over 320,000 users, we're more than just a ticketing platform - we bring you a way to keep nightlife exciting. Find the best parties, get unlimited access, and connect with other people to always party with someone new. Break the boring “same club, same people” circle.

Whether planning a memorable night out in Stockholm, a spontaneous party in Gothenburg, or looking for anything exciting across Scandinavia, Keyflow ensures you have the best access.

Party Mode: Dive deeper into the night with our unique social feature. Connect, chat, and plan your evening with other Keyflow users. Whether you're new in town or just looking to expand your friends' circle, Party Mode brings the party community to you.

For students, our 'Student Subscription' is a game-changer. Enjoy perks like permanent guest list access, free entries, bespoke discounts, and more. With Keyflow, every night is yours.

Businesses aren't left out either. 'Own the Night' is our bespoke initiative designed for companies looking to gift their employees an unmatched nightlife experience. After all, every employee deserves the best the city has to offer after work.

Feature highlights:

Tickets & Guest Lists: Browse the best events and venues in Scandinavia and get access effortlessly.

Party Mode: A dedicated space to connect with fellow party people, chat, and plan your night out together.

Tailored Subscriptions: Catering to diverse needs, from students to young professionals, we've got you covered with unlimited nightlife.

Nightlife can suck, we all know it, so let us make sure that you always have the best night possible without any effort.
descriptionShort: Turn your night into life!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: We made it easier for you to stay up-to-date with new in-app notifications related to subscriptions. Also, in this version we improved the subscription cards!
